node.text: * If you want to #levelup your fitness & physique after a setback, there's no better way than Pilates.  But leveling up isn't only about injury prevention, it's finding that confidence you get when you look good, feel great, and know you're about to perform at your best.  I'm partnering with @trojanbrandcondoms to launch their #UltraFit condoms because it's more than just protection that matters.  *  *  #TrojanULTRAFIT condoms are available exclusively at Walmart and if you buy in-store, you can enter the #UltraFitSweepstakes running from June 15- August 30 with weekly drawings to win big prizes that will level up your lifestyle. Hit the link in bio for details.   Also, throw a shout out in the comments and one you will have a chance for a meet and greet with me before the sweeps is over.            *  *   NO PURCHASE NECESSARY. Void where prohibited. Open to legal residents of the U.S. and D.C. 18 years or older and age of majority. Begins 06/15/2021 at 12:00:01 a.m. ET and ends on 08/31/21 at 11:59:59 p.m. ET. Prize/Odds: Total ARV of all Prizes up to $59,223.50. Odds of winning depend on the total number of eligible entries received. For Official Rules, complete details and how to enter without making a purchase, visit Rules.TrojanUltraFitSweeps.com. Sponsor: Church & Dwight, Co., Inc., Princeton South Corporate Center, 500 Charles Ewing Blvd., Ewing, NJ 08628
